#: ../bugfixes/type1/ivanbombsdisappearing.rst:9
msgid "Disappearing Ivan Bombs"
msgstr ""

#: ../bugfixes/type1/ivanbombsdisappearing.rst:11
msgid ""
"Ivan Bombs attached to a unit just vanished when the unit deployed into a"
" building and vice versa. The bomb would also disappear if a rigged "
"building changed its owner. If a building was sold while a bomb was "
"attached to it, the bomb was sold along with it, without being triggered."
msgstr ""

#: ../bugfixes/type1/ivanbombsdisappearing.rst:16
msgid ""
":game:`Ares` transfers the bomb in such cases and prevents the bomb from "
"getting lost in the process. If a unit or building is sold, the bomb will"
" now go off."
msgstr ""

